Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-You've got the wrong person!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.13,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
