Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's me...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm Akiba Kotarou, your substitute \Nmanager for today!
