Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so happy to see how lovely you are! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.35,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san told me to wear a disguise whenever I'm somewhere with a lot of people.{}
