Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all right. I screw up like that all the time.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
