Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The weather looks fine...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's have lunch here.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... used to be an adventurer.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've even climbed Mt. Everest.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, it should be ready.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so good!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm glad!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's plenty of it, so eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.02,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... why did you become a manager?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's my dream.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you're on an expedition...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There are often times when \Nthe going gets tough.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At those times...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...music brings you incredible strength...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To support those whose songs give courage to other people...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's my dream.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.16,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.38,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san, your dream is \Nto be a top singer, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dream, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not my only one, though...
