Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It really is...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Feels so good...
