Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like we might not be able to do this today. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No good...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if it can be fixed...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wanted to hear the songs...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right! I'll fix it!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Akiba-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should leave it alone...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san will be mad at you!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm good at video games. {shani: lol}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't think this is quite like a video game!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's funny...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.08,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.80,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscy110\fscx110}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... not much... just...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.10,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whoa!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The data for the songs has been totally erased!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.61,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How can you possibly make up for this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That was the data for the first album!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So sorry, Takasu-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san didn't do it on purpose!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Would it be better if he had done it on purpose?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why on earth is an incompetent guy like you a manager anyway?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're just going to screw up and cause other people problems...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...why don't you just quit now?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Get out of here! You're useless!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as Takasu-san says...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm just not fit to be a manager...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.99,0:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's how it really is...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Doesn't matter who's management it is I am assigned with... {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I mess up everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They always end up in failure...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The job with you today, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I told myself I would do my best from the start...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look how it ended up...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm hopeless, aren't I?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san, weren't you trying your best for me?! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just before...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You were only doing that because I said that I wanted to hear the songs...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I had many new experiences \Nwith you today, Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.21,0:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For me...{I, getting to play outside makes no dang sense, hence the edit}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Getting to play outside was always...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...something that I didn't get to do much...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I ate lunch like I was on a camping trip...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I got to run live I've never done before...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was really fun!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... don't say that.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, Akiba-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Forgive me...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.22,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's with that...?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter what... that substitute manager messes up way too much!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just like a certain someone...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm doing my best at my job as a Shinigami! {shani: Aww! Meroko! Takuto didn't even say the certain someone was you! <3}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.16,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He definitely works as hard \Nas he can, but still fails...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yey. Yep. I understand, like totally. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! Akiba-san?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry about everything yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... I've been doing some thinking...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I think I'll just quit working and go back to the countryside.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please don't say that you're quitting.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go and apologize to Takasu-san together.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.17,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as Takasu-san said.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I should stop being a manager.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When I'm around...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I just cause trouble for everybody.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have to leave for the station soon...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be late for my train...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscy90\fscx90}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscy90\fscx90}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Akiba-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello? Akiba-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.68,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san said that he quit!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have to go to the station fast!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Otherwise, we'll miss his train and \NTakasu-san will still be mad...{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... what should we do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto! {Shani: relying a bit too much on Takuto, eh?}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I got it. I got it already! Calm down!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.06,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.53,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have to hurry. {internal thought}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.07,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right. In a situation like this... {internal thought + edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}To gain some time...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}At the crossing, long jump!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}Long jump here too!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}Here we take a shortcut!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be5}Here, triple jump!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... {\alpha&Hff&}did it! {alpha time}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... did it! {alpha time}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscy110}{\fscx110}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}F-Full Moon{\i0}-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Akiba-san, don't quit.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You came all the way here to tell me that...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You mustn't quit, Akiba-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I'm around, I'm just a burden on everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That can't be...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... your dream to help singers...{}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're just going to give up on it?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fs30}From platform 23...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fs30}Train 21, bound for Komachi through Akita...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fs30}will be departing shortly...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.26,0:17:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fs30}In a short while... boarding will begin on platform 23.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... I'll get going.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You mustn't give up!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There might be many more hardships before your dream comes true...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But if you give up, then all hope is lost!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscy85\fscx85}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You mustn't give up!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's gone...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.36,0:18:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like a lot happened \Nwhile I was gone, Mitsuki. {shani: yay! Ooshige <3 is back!}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san seemed to be in a jam, too...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well... Luckily, the songs were saved in another computer.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So the songs weren't completely lost?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... just a copy...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's great...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.25,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait... Akiba-san didn't need to \Ngive up on his dream then...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you come with me for a bit today?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay. We're here.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san, what is this place..?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This will be a store that will sell {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  merchandise. {future tense, the place is still under construction, right?}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mine?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Manager, what about the cable here?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.60,0:19:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This area should be used for the display window...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So the cables should be on the other side, and install the switches there.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure, boss.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-{\alpha&Hff&}san... {alpha time}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.99,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san... {alpha time}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon-{\i0}san! Ooshige-senpai!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Welcome!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're the first customers.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You didn't go back to the countryside?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And... you're a manager?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as you said, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I mustn't give up, right?
